{"tid":635443,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登=今時今日既香港","createTime":"2018-04-20T06:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T23:26:09.000Z","uid":58335,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c8da2bd5e795e19a6bc0184d5be4915eb250f537","tid":635443,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"以前既香港百花齊放，咩思想，咩言論都有，創造力都好高<br />\n<br />\n以前既高登成日有新潮文，新改歌，好多潮語同文化都係出自高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今時今日既香港，講多兩句都話要拉要鎖，連戴妖都比人屈埋做港獨。創意方面亦少左好多，愈來愈多係抄返黎(當然有d係鄰國公司借香港名開公司)<br />\n<br />\n今時今日既連登，好似仲未見有咩新潮文，loop黎loop去都係高登個d，打潮文d 00後夠膽死咪你打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改歌亦唔見有特色，<br />\n連登文化可以話係咩都冇，最大文化就係 所有女人都係雞同男人就係臭鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以兩登文化同香港一樣，已長埋黃土，連匪搞分裂就係害人不淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37efc2377a17adb7494c2c67fe82845a8c327ac6","tid":635443,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83197ebf9dacb9d0c14d46a5cba210a5ecc8513f","tid":635443,"uid":91813,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"咁d潮文00後個時又未睇過 點會知 唔知問下有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申非00後"},{"pid":"ad15786ed33d0cc6f034117fc5a49178c7cfb40e","tid":635443,"uid":86893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:31:38.000Z","msg":"oldcf<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860698dc7236fbaedc9ee28d5e7c861e691c0d90","tid":635443,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83197ebf9dacb9d0c14d46a5cba210a5ecc8513f","tid":635443,